ection Agency, set a limit of 126 units per 100 milliliters of water and say that higher levels are not suitable for recreational use.\", \"from\": 5589, \"to\": 5781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5629, \"end\": 5660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Environmental_Protection_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6383761513133905e-27, \"text\": \"Environmental Protection Agency\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Environmental_Protection_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Environmental_Protection_Agency\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other organizations\", \"from\": 5589, \"to\": 5608}, {\"ngram\": \"a limit\", \"from\": 5666, \"to\": 5673}, {\"ngram\": \"126 units\", \"from\": 5677, \"to\": 5686}, {\"ngram\": \"100 milliliters\", \"from\": 5691, \"to\": 5706}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 5710, \"to\": 5715}, {\"ngram\": \"higher levels\", \"from\": 5729, \"to\": 5742}, {\"ngram\": \"recreational use\", \"from\": 5764, \"to\": 5780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In deciding whether events can be held in the river, World Triathlon's medical committee said it considers water quality analysis, sanitary inspection and the weather forecast.\", \"from\": 5783, \"to\": 5959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5836, \"end\": 5851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.511553130987277e-13, \"text\": \"World Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 5803, \"to\": 5809}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 5825, \"to\": 5834}, {\"ngram\": \"water quality analysis\", \"from\": 5890, \"to\": 5912}, {\"ngram\": \"sanitary inspection\", \"from\": 5914, \"to\": 5933}, {\"ngram\": \"the weather forecast\", \"from\": 5938, \"to\": 5958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A day after Wednesday's competitions in the Seine, data released by World Triathlon showed that a sample taken at 6 a.m. Wednesday at the Pont Alexandre III, the bridge where the swimming segment began and ended, showed a level of 249 units.\", \"from\": 5961, \"to\": 6202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6005, \"end\": 6010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999989067874, \"rank\": 1.0933904016993636e-09, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 6029, \"end\": 6044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.511553130987277e-13, \"text\": \"World Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\"}, {\"begin\": 6099, \"end\": 6117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_Alexandre_III\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pont Alexandre III\", \"types\": [\"Q12280\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_Alexandre_III\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_Alexandre_III\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wednesday's competitions\", \"from\": 5973, \"to\": 5997}, {\"ngram\": \"data\", \"from\": 6012, \"to\": 6016}, {\"ngram\": \"a sample\", \"from\": 6057, \"to\": 6065}, {\"ngram\": \"6 a.m.\", \"from\": 6075, \"to\": 6081}, {\"ngram\": \"the bridge\", \"from\": 6119, \"to\": 6129}, {\"ngram\": \"the swimming segment\", \"from\": 6136, \"to\": 6156}, {\"ngram\": \"a level\", \"from\": 6181, \"to\": 6188}, {\"ngram\": \"249 units\", \"from\": 6192, \"to\": 6201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Samples from other points along the course were at similar levels.\", \"from\": 6203, \"to\": 6269, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Samples\", \"from\": 6203, \"to\": 6210}, {\"ngram\": \"other points\", \"from\": 6216, \"to\": 6228}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 6235, \"to\": 6245}, {\"ngram\": \"similar levels\", \"from\": 6254, \"to\": 6268}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Are the tests used during the Games sufficient?\", \"from\": 6271, \"to\": 6318, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tests\", \"from\": 6275, \"to\": 6284}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 6297, \"to\": 6306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dan Angelescu, founder andCEOof Fluidion, a Paris and Los Angeles-based water monitoring tech company, says the tests have \\\"shortcomings\\\" and \\\"undercount severely the bacteria.\\\"\", \"from\": 6320, \"to\": 6497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6364, \"end\": 6369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8350356355766536e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dan Angelescu\", \"from\": 6320, \"to\": 6333}, {\"ngram\": \"founder andCEOof Fluidion\", \"from\": 6335, \"to\": 6360}, {\"ngram\": \"Los Angeles-based water monitoring tech company\", \"from\": 6374, \"to\": 6421}, {\"ngram\": \"the tests\", \"from\": 6428, \"to\": 6437}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"shortcomings\", \"from\": 6443, \"to\": 6456}, {\"ngram\": \"the bacteria\", \"from\": 6483, \"to\": 6495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fluidion is testing the water several times a day, and Angelescu said, \\\"What we see is that water quality is not as good as those measurement data that the city publishes,\\\" resulting in \\\"an underestimation of the actual risk.\\\"\", \"from\": 6499, \"to\": 6725, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fluidion\", \"from\": 6499, \"to\": 6507}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 6519, \"to\": 6528}, {\"ngram\": \"Angelescu\", \"from\": 6554, \"to\": 6563}, {\"ngram\": \"water quality\", \"from\": 6591, \"to\": 6604}, {\"ngram\": \"those measurement data\", \"from\": 6623, \"to\": 6645}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 6651, \"to\": 6659}, {\"ngram\": \"an underestimation\", \"from\": 6686, \"to\": 6704}, {\"ngram\": \"the actual risk\", \"from\": 6708, \"to\": 6723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The company measures both \\\"free floating\\\" bacteria in the water and takes a \\\"comprehensive\\\" level that Angelescu says also includes bacteria attached to fecal or sediment particles.\", \"from\": 6727, \"to\": 6908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The company\", \"from\": 6727, \"to\": 6738}, {\"ngram\": \"both \\\"free floating\\\" bacteria\", \"from\": 6748, \"to\": 6777}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 6781, \"to\": 6790}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"comprehensive\\\" level\", \"from\": 6801, \"to\": 6824}, {\"ngram\": \"Angelescu\", \"from\": 6830, \"to\": 6839}, {\"ngram\": \"bacteria\", \"from\": 6859, \"to\": 6867}, {\"ngram\": \"fecal or sediment particles\", \"from\": 6880, \"to\": 6907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said the comprehensive count provides a more complete picture than the lab test the city is using.\", \"from\": 6909, \"to\": 7010, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the comprehensive count\", \"from\": 6917, \"to\": 6940}, {\"ngram\": \"a more complete picture\", \"from\": 6950, \"to\": 6973}, {\"ngram\": \"the lab test\", \"from\": 6979, \"to\": 6991}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 6992, \"to\": 7000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He likened it to watching a busy road with pedestrians, motorcycles, cars and buses and trying to count all the people.\", \"from\": 7012, \"to\": 7131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a busy road\", \"from\": 7038, \"to\": 7049}, {\"ngram\": \"pedestrians\", \"from\": 7055, \"to\": 7066}, {\"ngram\": \"motorcycles\", \"from\": 7068, \"to\": 7079}, {\"ngram\": \"cars\", \"from\": 7081, \"to\": 7085}, {\"ngram\": \"buses\", \"from\": 7090, \"to\": 7095}, {\"ngram\": \"all the people\", \"from\": 7116, \"to\": 7130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The city's met